print a copy of the winning ticket then gave it to mark s herbst 
state attorney general leroy s zimmerman said at a news conference 
today 
the ticket listed the winning numbers for the super 7 lottery 
drawing last july 15 one winning ticket to that jackpot was sold 
statewide but the winner had never claimed the prize 
