the precursor to the japanese meeting 
eastland said department regulations allow for payments for 
spouses to be reimbursed by an outside entity profitmaking or 
nonprofit making if certain conditions are met in this case the 
conditions were met he said 
swanson said the cost for the china meeting including 
transportation was about 2500 the registration fee there was 
400 
meeses expenses for the japan trip will be picked up by the 
government since he is making an official visit at the invitation 
